{"tid":170073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"義士最終被港豬出賣","createTime":"2017-03-24T14:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T16:07:02.000Z","uid":4672,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9da42b745fcc8c129d394c3a34eb7d5445e6dfb3","tid":170073,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:01:36.000Z","msg":"致雨革,旺角義士：<br />\n<br />\n       您們在獄中還過得好嗎？身體舊傷康復了嗎？<br />\n我係社會遊民,今次想同您地匯報香港最新情況.<br />\n<br />\n        雖然當年泛民否決了831決定,但現在他們覺得小圈子選舉不錯 有得參與 有得投票(好似係),市民們紛紛上街支持候選人,對他們來講普選好似可有可無.最重要係支持薯片叔叔,不論是他的慈祥外表,還是政綱中的23條.大家打成一片 不亦樂乎,似乎早以忘記當年為何要反對小圈子選舉 要反對831框架<br />\n   <br />\n     沒錯⋯佢地接受了這個小圈子選舉⋯<br />\n<br />\n     我地不知道要如何向我地下一代交代,和當年97的大人們一樣 什麼都冇做 僅僅係請求港共政府賣港不要賣得太快,因此泛民努力地推薯片叔叔上位,各民主派也不忘繼續內訌,互相攻擊.亦看不到香港的未來<br />\n      很多年輕人因此輕生,我地除了恥笑鄙視和rip之外,什麼都做不到<br />\n<br />\n      對唔住 我地放棄了抗爭 辜負了您地一番心血 出賣了您地對香港既愛 仲斷送了您地前途 選擇向中共妥協  在被強姦著同時又享受著 .我地冇面向下一代交代 更冇臉面對您們<br />\n<br />\n      曾幾何時 他們講過 他們是義士們最堅挺的後盾<br />\n會一直支持著你地 相信著你地 <br />\n     曾幾何時 他們講過 遇到什麼困難會幫助你地<br />\n現在,我地捐出既錢不知所終 想為您地請更好的律師也沒有資金 能夠做的就是看著港豬們開心地參與著小圈子選舉 將當年我們之間的約定一一打破<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n致此 勇敢的香港義士<br />\n<br />\n                                                社會遊民<br />\n2017年3月24日"},{"pid":"76e073de2408a44aba7e218a472663863d4dd71c","tid":170073,"uid":53698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:06:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0UprhqDTE58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0UprhqDTE58&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=c29d3943\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0UprhqDTE58</a><br />\n諗起呢條雨革無耐出既片<br />\n 講香港人盲目妥協 無下限既底線<br />\n2年多啲 條片依然適用 說明經過左咁多人 <br />\n香港人都仲未進步反思 汲取教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959507894d4d9d78190b7dda6f14ae445b9c0fbc","tid":170073,"uid":53698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/0UprhqDTE58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0UprhqDTE58&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=c29d3943\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0UprhqDTE58</a><br />\n諗起呢條雨革無耐出既片<br />\n 講香港人盲目妥協 無下限既底線<br />\n2年多啲 條片依然適用 說明經過左咁多<span style=\"color: red;\">事</span><br />\n香港人都仲未進步反思 汲取教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"55832649b92b95ad638138ad33c1427994e2517c","tid":170073,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:07:03.000Z","msg":"同時希望自殺者早日安息 <br />\n來世不要做香港人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b964845e8646d7c3b85f81e1ca444ee9f5a367e","tid":170073,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:10:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1cf929b50133ab82946e146949b6df5a50c2a9","tid":170073,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"矯情"},{"pid":"642f42f5cc2caeb27d50eef14fc12c5f58797dba","tid":170073,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:13:24.000Z","msg":"可能港豬早已忘記你地對香港既付出<br />\n<br />\n但我 社會遊民 永遠不會忘記你地<br />\n<br />\n因為你地先係真正既香港人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3274e5f17d955132f520d72ade3ea7492a5b259a","tid":170073,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e064e3d02041d278d7e8cab4f7b554e362ec20a7","tid":170073,"uid":87064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c216ac3a191f45bdb2c5cf6508267ae49917a66","tid":170073,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253879f6b8b22fd8cabbd49eeb525831992710c9","tid":170073,"uid":77697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd34da2293bf900ee09e16e6f415eb601f1bb325","tid":170073,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:20:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>矯情</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我實在冇辦法忘記班義士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c8bc4986f954014cad2826c060552d24aa87c4","tid":170073,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:25:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PTcIqM35Cy4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPTcIqM35Cy4&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=6f4fa595\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PTcIqM35Cy4</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd524de3ae730f8fbb3fb2cbe7999aa7b515bab","tid":170073,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:31:15.000Z","msg":"做豬好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2baf99cc844a276b87fc2c31017496312d0b66a9","tid":170073,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:31:39.000Z","msg":"SocREC 社會記錄頻道<br />\n23 mins &middot; <br />\n24mar2017（19:18） 中環<br />\n特首候選人曾俊華集氣大會尾聲，曾生提到兩年半前旁邊龍和道的佔中事件,並說要為今晚的相聚賦予呢度新的意義.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/socrec/videos/1715132501847007/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsocrec%2Fvideos%2F1715132501847007%2F&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=868de101\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/socrec/videos/1715132501847007/</a><br />\n<br />\n當日義士被鎖, 被拉, 被打, 既龍和道, 一個香港人曾經流過血淚既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719a0e7efc0601ba9a7e1bd458223f15e8e8c66a","tid":170073,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:33:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>SocREC 社會記錄頻道<br />\n23 mins &middot; <br />\n24mar2017（19:18） 中環<br />\n特首候選人曾俊華集氣大會尾聲，曾生提到兩年半前旁邊龍和道的佔中事件,並說要為今晚的相聚賦予呢度新的意義.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/socrec/videos/1715132501847007/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsocrec%2Fvideos%2F1715132501847007%2F&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=868de101\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/socrec/videos/1715132501847007/</a><br />\n<br />\n當日義士被鎖, 被拉, 被打, 既龍和道, 一個香港人曾經流過血淚既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n23條 不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d59cabbbe11a0e623985a2d2dd7ffd3c014f86","tid":170073,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:33:45.000Z","msg":"算啦，都唔係第一次。港豬終會俾現實懲罰，堅毅嘅義士終會得到勝利"},{"pid":"cd4fb77224db62b7fa8641ea8b953dfd69ea6730","tid":170073,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:36:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算啦，都唔係第一次。港豬終會俾現實懲罰，堅毅嘅義士終會得到勝利</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地得到的只有案底同傷疤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab8c09c767e10224e34f8582c716097cb6a3b88","tid":170073,"uid":66217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:39:25.000Z","msg":"幾時同一陣線過"},{"pid":"0470d6ab0daae7084e8c2eda12d668485ea9bfa4","tid":170073,"uid":34033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484b5a774394c859c7a29e54af6ae19c5edd0bc7","tid":170073,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:40:33.000Z","msg":"依家睇翻當年義士俾黑警打d片<br />\n一支支警棍仆落個頭 仆落個身<br />\n胡椒噴霧兜